ider.com%2Fremote-jobs-schedule-errands-leisure-during-work-hours-2023-3%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Btriple%20peak%26quot%3B%20workday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-remote-work-changed-economy-pandemic-2023-4%5C%22%3Eits%20effects%20on%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20reconfigured%20the%20white-collar%20employee's%20workday%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20including%20by%20changing%20what%20time%20of%20day%20they're%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManagers%20are%20reporting%20a%20%26quot%3Bdead%20zone%26quot%3B%20from%204%20pm%20to%206%20pm%2C%20when%20workers%20are%20signing%20off%20early%20before%20logging%20on%20again%20later%20to%20wrap%20up%20their%20work%20for%20the%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fwork-office-coworkers-schedule-meetings-2af3f9b0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20reported.%20Workers%20are%20using%20the%20time%20to%20run%20errands%2C%20pick%20up%20their%20kids%2C%20commute%20home%20before%20rush%20hour%2C%20or%20use%20the%20time%20for%20leisurely%20purposes%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnbloom.people.stanford.edu%2Fsites%2Fg%2Ffiles%2Fsbiybj24291%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Ffile%2Fgolfingfromhome.pdf%5C%22%3Ehitting%20the%20golf%20course%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btriple%20peak%26quot%3B%20day%2C%20as%20The%20Atlantic's%20Derek%20Thompson%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fnewsletters%2Farchive%2F2022%2F04%2Ftriple-peak-day-work-from-home%2F629457%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20April.%20In%20a%20study%20that%20year%2C%20Microsoft%20researchers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D569a91d5c4ba5f6d5b2eddff0807736f219e5a1866d33f114dc02ba33753c1fa%26postID%3D64ba8eaa818c7a7ff1df4709