Insider%20obtained%20a%20guest%20list%20for%20a%202017%20event%20on%20%26quot%3BBillionaire%20Mountain%26quot%3B%20that%20featured%20top%20judges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELaw%20firms%20paid%20%2410%2C000%20a%20year%20for%20access%20to%20such%20exclusive%20gatherings%20%E2%80%93%20and%20their%20clients%20came%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeryl%20Chertoff%20introduced%20Kagan%20that%20night.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Michael%20Chertoff%2C%20later%20worked%20for%20SCOTUS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChampagne%20flowed%20at%20a%202017%20Aspen%20Institute%20event%2C%20held%20at%20a%20mansion%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fphotos-aspen-red-mountain-nicknamed-billionaire-mountain-neighborhood-colorado-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBillionaire%20Mountain%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20%2410%2C000-year%20donors%20and%20their%20guests%20rubbed%20shoulders%20with%20some%20of%20the%20nation's%20most%20powerful%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aspen%20Institute%20promises%20%26quot%3Bexclusive%20access%20to%20high-level%20gatherings%26quot%3B%20for%20donors%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspeninstitute.org%2Fprograms%2Fjustice-and-society-program%2Fjustice-circle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJustice%20Circle%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%202017%20%26quot%3Bspeakers%20dinner%26quot%3B%20featuring%20Justice%20Elena%20Kagan%20was%20as%20exclusive%20as%20they%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%2050%20attendees%20RSVP'd%2C%20according%20to%20two%20guest%20lists%20obtained%20by%20Insider.%20Corporate%20execs%20and%20lawyers%20with%20business%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20mingled%20with%20some%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20influential%20jurists.%20While%20Kagan%20was%20a%20guest%20of%20honor%2C%20Brett%20Kavanaugh%2C%20at%20the%20time%20a%20judge%20on%20the%20DC%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%2C%20was%20also%20present.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20President%20Trump%20nominated%20Kavanaugh%20to%20join%20Kagan%20on%20the%20nation's%20highest%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hospitality%20provided%20to%20the%20judges%20wasn't%20anywhere%20near%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20decadeslong%20relationship%20between%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20and%20the%20billionaire%20real-estate%20developer%20Harlan%20Crow.%20Kagan's%20visit%20to%20Aspen%20had%20a%20public%20component%2C%20and%20both%20she%20and%20Kavanaugh%20documented%20that%20the%20Aspen%20Institue%20provided%20free%20travel%20and%20lodging%20for%20the%20event%20on%20their%20annual%20disclosure%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20guest%20lists%20do%20show%20is%20the%20economy%20of%20access%20and%20influence%20that%20has%20sprung%20up%20around%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Revelations%20about%20Thomas%20and%20Crow's%20relationship%20have%20prompted%20calls%20in%20Congress%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20adopt%20its%20first-ever%20binding%20code%20of%20ethics.%20Kagan's%20appearance%20as%20an%20apparent%20guest%20of%20honor%20could%20violate%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscourts.gov%2Fjudges-judgeships%2Fcode-conduct-united-states-judges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECode%20of%20Conduct%20for%20federal%20judges%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20bars%20judges%20from%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bspeaker%2C%20a%20guest%20of%20honor%2C%20or%20featured%20on%20the%20program%26quot%3B%20of%20fundraising%20events.%20But%20as%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%2C%20Kagan%20is%20not%20currently%20bound%20by%20those%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bans%20justices%20from%20attending%20fundraising%20events%2C%20but%20it%20defines%20them%20to%20include%20only%20events%20that%20raise%20more%20money%20than%20they%20spend%20or%20where%20there%20is%20a%20specific%20solicitation%20for%20funds%2C%20Kathleen%20Clark%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20government%20ethics%20at%20Washington%20University%20in%20St.%20Louis%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20not%20violate%20those%20rules%20as%20the%20rules%20have%20been%20narrowly%20interpreted%2C%20but%20nonetheless%2C%20there%20still%20is%20a%20problem%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20call%20this%20event%20anything%20but%20a%20reward%20for%20having%20given%20money%20to%20the%20organization%3F%20A%20bonus%20awarded%20to%20those%20who%20have%20already%20generously%20contributed%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20than%20a%20hypothetical%20ethics%20violation%2C%20what%20the%20guest%20list%20reveals%20is%20the%20perfectly%20legal%20way%20in%20which%20the%20power%20of%20the%20nation's%20highest%20court%20is%20marketed%20by%20third%20parties%20as%20a%20chance%20to%20pay%20for%20face-to-face%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverybody%20got%20something%3A%20Kagan%20and%20Kavanaugh%20got%20a%20free%20trip%20to%20a%20luxurious%20destination%2C%20Aspen%20got%20money%20from%20donors%2C%20and%20those%20donors%20got%20privileged%20access%20to%20Kagan%20and%20Kavanaugh%20%E2%80%94%20an%20intimate%20dinner%20setting%20where%20the%20two%20jurists%2C%20no%20longer%20ensconced%20by%20their%20chambers%2C%20clerks%2C%20and%20robes%2C%20were%20more%20approachable%20than%20they%20would%20be%20in%20any%20official%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20face%20time%20with%20a%20justice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKagan's%20admirers%20like%20to%20recall%20the%20time%20she%20turned%20down%20a%20proposed%20gift%20of%20lox%20and%20bagels%20from%20a%20group%20of%20her%20high-school%20friends%20as%20evidence%20of%20her%20stringent%20approach%20to%20ethics.%20But%20the%20evening%20at%20the%20Aspen%20Institute%20demonstrates%20a%20willingness%20to%20mingle%20with%20VIPs%20who%20were%20only%20there%20because%20they'd%20shelled%20out%20five%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEleven%20of%20the%2050%20names%20listed%20as%20attendees%20at%20the%20dinner%20were%20guests%20of%20law%20firms.%20They%20included%20in-house%20lawyers%20for%20the%20coal%20giant%20Peabody%20Energy%20and%20the%20convenience-store%20chain%20Speedway%2C%20both%20guests%20of%20the%20law%20firm%20Shook%2C%20Hardy%20%26amp%3B%20Bacon.%20Tristan%20Duncan%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Aspen%20Institute's%20Justice%20Circle%20and%20a%20partner%20at%20Shook%2C%20who%20was%20also%20at%20the%20dinner%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shb.com%2Fnews%2F2016%2F02%2Fsupreme-court-blocks-epa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erepresented%20Peabody%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202016%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shb.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F03%2Fnews-cy-pres-case-duncan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpeedway%20in%202018%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTristan%20Duncan%20may%20be%20supplying%20names%20for%202-3%20additional%20guests%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20lists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aspen%20Institute%2C%20Duncan%2C%20Peabody%2C%20and%20Speedway%20did%20not%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20Insider%2C%20some%20attendees%20said%20that%20they%20didn't%20remember%20much%20of%20the%20event%2C%20and%20that%20nothing%20inappropriate%20had%20happened.%20Christina%20Sullivan%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20a%20company%20that%20runs%20apartment%20complexes%20called%20Gables%20Residential%2C%20said%20that%20her%20interaction%20with%20Kagan%20was%20limited%20to%20a%20handshake%20and%20a%20greeting.%26quot%3Bshak%5Bing%5D%20her%20hand%20and%20say%5Bing%5D%20hello.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20all%20up%20in%20arms%20%E2%80%94%20the%20court%2C%20privilege%2C%20whatever%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20think%20you're%20barking%20up%20the%20wrong%20tree%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brian%20O'Connor%2C%20a%20real-estate%20businessman%20whose%20mother%2C%20the%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Sandra%20Day%20O'Connor%2C%20was%20being%20honored%20at%20the%20Aspen%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20hobnobbing%20with%20judges%20can%20give%20lawyers%20and%20litigants%20flashes%20of%20insight%20into%20their%20values%20and%20personalities%20with%20a%20candor%20and%20clarity%20unavailable%20to%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuslim%20Lakhani%2C%20a%20Washington%20businessman%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20chatted%20with%20Kagan%20about%20judges%20and%20%26quot%3Bjudicial%20activism%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20native%20Pakistan.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Kagan%20seemed%20to%20invoke%20a%20higher%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20a%20judgment%20is%20made%2C%20after%20that%2C%20there's%20only%20one%20court.%20That's%20up%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Kagan%20said%2C%20according%20to%20Lakhani's%20recollection.%20Kagan%2C%20Lakhani%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bkeeps%20that%20front%20and%20center%20in%20her%20mind%2C%20something%20like%20'I%20must%20pass%20laws%20that%20are%20correct%2C%20because%20I%20have%20to%20answer%20for%20the%20judgments%20that%20I%20give.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kagan%20has%20also%20spoken%20about%20her%20faith%20in%20public%20settings%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20litigator%20who%20wouldn't%20jump%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20have%20an%20informal%20back-and-forth%20with%20her%20away%20from%20the%20cameras%2C%20as%20Lakhani%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKagan%20and%20Kavanaugh%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20made%20with%20the%20court's%20public-information%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20uneasy%20intersection%20of%20friendship%20and%20self-interest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20the%20Aspen%20dinner%2C%20Meryl%20Chertoff%20introduced%20Kagan%20before%20a%20public%20conversation.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Chertoff%2C%20a%20law%20professor%2C%20headed%20the%20Aspen%20Institute's%20Justice%20and%20Society%20Program.%20In%202010%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DemFlq9Ng9DE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Espoke%20favorably%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Kagan's%20nomination%20to%20the%20highest%20court.%20As%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Aspen%20Institute's%20Justice%20and%20Society%20Program%20at%20the%20time%2C%20which%20was%20hosting%20Kagan%2C%20she%20likely%20would%20have%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20shaping%20the%20VIP%20guest%20list%20for%20the%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Chertoff%2C%20a%20former%20appeals%20judge%20who%20was%20the%20secretary%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20under%20George%20W.%20Bush%2C%20accompanied%20his%20wife%20to%20that%20dinner.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20year%20after%20the%20Aspen%20dinner%2C%20Michael%20Chertoff's%20consulting%20company%2C%20Chertoff%20Group%2C%20started%20working%20directly%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20That%20relationship%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F03%2F21%2Fsupreme-court-michael-chertoff-00088119%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewasn't%20made%20public%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20this%20year.%20CNN%20reported%20that%20the%20Chertoff%20Group%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F01%2F27%2Fpolitics%2Fsupreme-court-chertoff-leak-investigation%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebilled%20upward%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%241%20million%2C%20money%20that%20ultimately%20came%20from%20taxpayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20from%20Congress%2C%20Michael%20Chertoff%20explained%20that%20he'd%20advised%20the%20court%20on%20security%20and%20on%20a%20pandemic-response%20plan.%20When%20asked%20if%20he%20maintained%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20relationships%26quot%3B%20with%20any%20justices%2C%20Chertoff%20wrote%20that%20he%20did%20not%20have%20%26quot%3Bongoing%20or%20regular%20social%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20he%20said%20there%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Boccasional%20social%20exchanges%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20at%20widely%20attended%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20Michael%20Chertoff%20interacted%20with%20either%20justice%20at%20the%20dinner%2C%20or%20whether%20there%20is%20any%20connection%20between%20the%20event%20and%20his%20later%20work%20for%20the%20court%2C%20which%20was%20handled%20not%20by%20Kagan%20or%20Kavanaugh%2C%20but%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20John%20Roberts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20presence%20of%20so%20many%20wealthy%20and%20influential%20people%20who%20might%20want%20something%20from%20the%20court%20is%20itself%20a%20problem%2C%20Gabe%20Roth%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20advocacy%20group%20Fix%20the%20Court%2C%20said.%20Roth%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20access%20economy%20can%20create%20the%20appearance%20of%20conflicts%20of%20interests%2C%20and%20said%20that%20judges%20should%20recuse%20themselves%20from%20cases%20involving%20firms%20or%20clients%20who%20pay%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20to%20meet%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20that%20Washington%20is%20a%20chummy%20town%20and%20more%20resources%20for%20Court%20security%20is%20likely%20warranted%2C%26quot%3B%20Roth%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BBut%20by%20the%20same%20token%2C%20given%20the%20ties%20between%20Chertoff%20and%20the%20justices%2C%20the%20notoriously%20opaque%20institution%20should%20open%20up%20its%20books%20to%20reassure%20the%20public%20that%20Chertoff's%20work%20was%20above%20board.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAccess%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20justices%20is%20used%20to%20reward%20donors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20ProPublica's%20reporting%20on%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fclarence-thomas-scotus-undisclosed-luxury-travel-gifts-crow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20undisclosed%20gifts%20and%20financial%20ties%20between%20Thomas%20and%20Crow%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20captured%20headlines%2C%20increasing%20attention%20is%20turning%20to%20other%20ways%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%20gain%20access%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aspen%20Institute%20isn't%20alone%20in%20dangling%20Supreme%20Court%20access%20to%20lure%20deep-pocketed%20donors.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F12%2F30%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fsupreme-court-historical-society-donors-justices.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReporting%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20that%20Rob%20Schenck%20used%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Historical%20Society%20as%20a%20springboard%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20conservative%20justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-nonprofit-anti-abortion-access-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInsider%20analysis%20of%20Historical%20Society%20donor%20and%20event%20records%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20a%20suite%20of%20archconservative%20activists%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20anti-abortion%20philanthropist%20and%20Domino's%20founder%20Tom%20Monaghan%2C%20the%20former%20Trump%20attorney%20Jay%20Sekulow%2C%20and%20the%20QAnon%20proponent%20and%20election%20denier%20Sidney%20Powell%20%E2%80%94%20had%20used%20the%20society%20as%20a%20vehicle%20to%20gain%20face%20time%20with%20the%20justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsupreme-court-ethics-donors-politics-4b6dc4ae23aac75d4fccb1bcff0b7e0b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%20exposed%3