Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20about%20hiring%20an%20SEO%20expert%20to%20help%20me%2C%20but%20the%20ones%20I%20contacted%20charged%20around%20%242%2C000.%20Instead%2C%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20me%20optimize%20my%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20asked%20for%20SEO%20key%20words%20to%20use%20for%20a%20maid-of-honor%20speech-writing%20service.%20I%20then%20used%20those%20words%20throughout%20my%20website's%20landing%20page%20and%20in%20blog%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20gaining%20traffic%20again%2C%20even%20with%20new%20competitors%20popping%20up.%20A%20few%20months%20after%20making%20these%20changes%2C%20my%20bookings%20climbed%20back%20to%20around%20five%20to%20seven%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20I%20leaned%20on%20ChatGPT%20for%20social%20media%20help%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20hired%20freelance%20social-media%20consultants%20before%20for%20anywhere%20between%20%241%2C500%20to%20%243%2C000%20a%20month%20to%20help%20me%20strategize%20content%20and%20even%20post%20for%20me.%20It%20took%20me%20anywhere%20from%2010%20to%2020%20hours%20to%20onboard%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20I%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20me%20brainstorm%20content%20for%20static%20Instagram%20posts%20and%20TikTok%20videos.%20I%20asked%20the%20tool%20to%20share%20a%20script%20to%20use%20when%20a%20person%20wants%20to%20turn%20down%20being%20a%20bridesmaid%20but%20feels%20awkward%20doing%20so.%20I%20used%20that%20script%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt_-SFigNNu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igshid%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReel%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20generated%20over%206%20million%20views%2C%20which%20is%20a%20record%20amount%20of%20views%20for%20my%20Instagram%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20used%20the%20tool%20to%20help%20me%20think%20of%20captions%20for%20posts.%20I%20had%20a%20folder%20of%20photos%20I%20was%20waiting%20to%20post%20on%20Instagram%20and%20videos%20based%20on%20TikTok%20trends%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20clever%20and%20engaging%20captions%20to%20use.%20Instead%20of%20carving%20out%20the%20time%20to%20write%20them%2C%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20create%20a%20caption%20for%20a%20video%20about%20being%20a%20bridesmaid%20by%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BHelp%20me%20end%20this%20caption.%20'When%20you've%20been%20a%20bridesmaid%20six%20times%20already%20this%20year%20and%20____.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20generated%20%26quot%3Band%20your%20bank%20account%20is%20crying%20for%20a%20break.%26quot%3B%20I%20used%20that%20as%20a%20text%20overlay%20to%20a%20prerecorded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ft%2FZT8RSrubX%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20created%20using%20trending%20a%20TikTok%20audio%2C%20and%20it%20performed%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20find%20the%20best%20hashtags%20to%20use%20for%20content%20about%20being%20a%20bridesmaid%20on%20TikTok.%20When%20I%20used%20hashtags%20for%20%26quot%3Bcatching%20the%20bouquet%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20a%20constant%20bridesmaid%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20noticed%20more%20engagement%20on%20those%20videos%20than%20I%20had%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I've%20used%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fall-hashtag.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20hashtag%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%2C%20ChatGPT%20cut%20down%20my%20research%20time%20by%2075%25%20and%20provided%20me%20with%20more%20thoughtful%20hashtags%20than%20the%20generic%20ones%20that%20other%20platforms%20can%20spit%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20I%20asked%20it%20to%20help%20me%20write%20pitch%20emails%20for%20brand%20sponsors%20and%20partners%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20biggest%20sources%20of%20income%20is%20brand%20deals%20and%20partnerships.%20Companies%20will%20pay%2