ider.com%2Fcelebrities-elon-musk-cant-dodge-jet-tracking-twitter-accounts-ladd-2022-10%5C%22%3Ewill%20not%20display%20LADD-identified%20planes.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ultra-rich%20can%20go%20one%20step%20further%20and%20completely%20shadow%20their%20tail%20numbers%20thanks%20to%20a%20second%20federal%20program%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fair_traffic%2Ftechnology%2Fequipadsb%2Fprivacy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivacy%C2%A0ICAO%C2%A0aircraft%20address%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20PIA%20%E2%80%94%20over%20300%20of%20which%20have%20been%20registered%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20workaround%20for%20both.%20Trackers%20can%20use%20an%20aircraft%20system%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fabout%2Foffice_org%2Fheadquarters_offices%2Favs%2Foffices%2Fafx%2Fafs%2Fafs400%2Fafs410%2Fads-b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EADS-B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20broadcasts%20information%20like%20GPS%20location%2C%20altitude%2C%20and%20speed%20from%20one%20aircraft%20to%20ground%20stations%20and%20other%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20this%20system%2C%20volunteers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20have%20set%20up%20radios%20that%20transfer%20flight%20data%20to%20a%20free%20public%20website%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobe.adsbexchange.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EADS-B%20Exchange%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20website%20collects%20the%20data%20and%20displays%20the%20locations%20of%20planes%20all%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-appears-use-faa-tool-block-jet-tracking-twitter-2022-10%5C%22%3ELADD%20and%20PIA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20the%20website%20that%20powered%20Sweeney's%20Twitter%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20privacy%20mitigation%20programs%20are%20effective%20for%20real