%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fgovt-blocks-1-billion-bid-by-china-s-byd-to-set-up-ev-factory-in-india-123072400352_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fgovt-blocks-1-billion-bid-by-china-s-byd-to-set-up-ev-factory-in-india-123072400352_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fgovt-blocks-1-billion-bid-by-china-s-byd-to-set-up-ev-factory-in-india-123072400352_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Manipur%3A%20%E2%80%98Horrific%20Videos%2C%20Reports%20Just%20Tip%20of%20Iceberg%2C%20Much%20More%20Has%20Happened%20We%20Don't%20Know%20About%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24140721%2FKT-22B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20author%2C%20journalist%20and%20consultant%20for%20several%20Christian%20television%20channels%20who%20was%20recently%20in%20Manipur%2C%20both%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20and%20spoke%20widely%20to%20people%20of%20both%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%2C%20says%20that%20the%20horrifying%20videos%20and%20reports%20that%20surfaced%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20killings%2C%20burning%20and%20rapes%20are%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%E2%80%9D.%20Babu%20Verghese%20says%20that%20the%20full%20truth%2C%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20known%2C%20will%20be%20far%20worse%20than%20what%20we%20know%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Verghese%20spoke%20of%20a%20young%20Kuki%20woman%20living%20in%20Imphal%20with%20her%20two-year-old%20child%20and%20separated%20from%20her%20husband%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20last%2082%20days%20hiding%20in%20fear%20that%20she%20could%20be%20targeted%20and%20killed.%20Verghese%20claims%20she%20is%20still%20in%20hiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20of%20Kuki%20villages%20where%20bodies%20of%20the%20dead%20were%20left%20unburied%20and%2C%20as%20he%20put%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20dogs%20had%20a%20heyday%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%2C%20whilst%20in%20Manipur%2C%20he%20had%20heard%20about%20reports%20of%20an%20attack%20by%20a%20Meitei%20mob%20in%20Khamenlok%20around%20the%20middle%20of%20June%20and%20the%20retaliation%2Fdefence%20by%20the%20Kuki%20which%2C%20allegedly%2C%20resulted%20in%20tens%20or%20even%20hundreds%20of%20deaths%2C%20Verghese%20said%20he%20had%20heard%20these%20reports%20from%20several%20sources%20but%20could%20not%20confirm%20them.%20Presumably%20this%20is%20one%20story%2C%20if%20true%2C%20that%20we%20still%20have%20to%20find%20out%20about%20and%20the%20details%20of%20which%20could%20be%20deeply%20disturbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3x6ZE3TB4Y8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20churches%2C%20Verghese%20said%20he%20had%20seen%20at%20least%20ten%20that%20have%20been%20destroyed%20in%20Imphal%20but%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20were%20several%20that%20are%20functioning%20and%20holding%20services.%20Verghese%20confirmed%20he%20had%20been%20reliably%20told%20that%20at%20least%20four%20Meitei%20churches%20have%20been%20destroyed%20in%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20violence%2C%20raping%20and%20killing%20was%20one-sided%2C%20Verghese%20said%20that%20both%20communities%20were%20doing%20it%20although%2C%20he%20added%2C%20the%20Kuki%20claim%20they%20are%20only%20responding%20in%20self-defence%20or%20in%20retaliation%20for%20an%20attack.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20Kuki%20have%20repeatedly%20told%20him%20they%20do%20not%20target%20women%20and%20children%20and%20that%20they%20have%20not%20indulged%20in%20raping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVerghese%20denied%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Meitei%20organisation%2C%20COCOMI%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%2023%20July%20to%20the%20President%20of%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CMeitei%20Christians%20are%20being%20ethnically%20cleansed%20%E2%80%A6%20from%20Churachandpur%2C%20Saikul%20and%20Kangpokpi%20districts%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20what%20is%20true%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20there%20are%20no%20Meitei%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20no%20Kuki%20in%20the%20valley%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20is%20effective%20demographic%20and%20geographical%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Verghese%20said%20he%20had%20personally%20witnessed%20bulldozers%20demolishing%20Meitei%20homes%20in%20what%20he%20called%20Lamka%2C%20the%20Kuki%20name%20for%20Churachandpur.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20was%20told%20the%20Meitei%20residents%20of%20those%20homes%20had%20already%20left.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20there%20was%20no%20way%20of%20verifying%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVerghese%20spoke%20about%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20who%20have%20set%20up%20roadblocks%20and%20frequently%2C%20he%20said%2C%20extort%20money.%20He%20spoke%20of%20a%20certain%20Father%20Johnson%20who%20had%20all%20his%20money%20taken%20by%20the%20Meira%20Paibi.%20Verghese%20said%20he%20was%20reliably%20told%20that%20this%20money%20is%20used%20to%20purchase%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Verghese%20denied%20reports%20that%20the%20Manipur%20police%20had%20handed%20over%20their%20weapons%20to%20militants%20whether%20Kuki%20or%20Meitei.%20He%20said%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20true.%20The%20police%20were%20overwhelmed%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20they%20could%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690187958000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24140721%2FKT