r%20Marshalled%20Out%20Of%20Assembly%20After%20Taking%20On%20Ashok%20Gehlot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERecently%20sacked%20Rajasthan%20minister%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Gudha%20was%20today%20marshalled%20out%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20after%20he%20took%20on%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20and%20tried%20to%20present%20a%20%26quot%3Bred%20diary%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20claims%20can%20be%20politically%20explosive.%C2%A0The%20Rajasthan%20assembly%20was%20adjourned%20after%20Mr%20Gudha%2C%20aided%20by%20BJP%20MLAs%2C%20created%20unruly%20scenes%20in%20the%20House%20during%20Zero%20Hour.%20The%20sacked%20minister%20tried%20to%20re-enter%20the%20Assembly%20forcibly%2C%20but%20was%20stopped%20at%20the%20entrance%2C%20visuals%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Congress%20leader%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Gudha%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20today%20after%20being%20removed%20as%20minister%20in%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20cabinet.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaMVOt0JRbM%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaMVOt0JRbM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20MP%2FCG%2FRajasthan%20(%40ANI_MP_CG_RJ)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI_MP_CG_RJ%2Fstatus%2F1683375294286299136%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gudha%20reached%20near%20Speaker%20CP%20Joshi's%20chair%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bred%20diary%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20an%20argument%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diary%20was%20allegedly%20recovered%20by%20Mr%20Gudha%20in%20the%20past%20during%20an%20IT%20raid%20on%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20associate%2C%20Dharmendra%20Singh%20Rathore.%20The%20sacked%20former%20minister%20says%20it%20could%20%26quot%3Bexpose%26quot%3B%20M