0Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20amid%20a%20face-off%20in%20Parliament%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20over%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20suspended%20for%20allegedly%20jumping%20into%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20and%20raising%20slogans%2C%20and%20refusing%20to%20go%20back%20despite%20being%20warned%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%2C%20which%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20have%20locked%20horns%20over%20the%20Centre's%20ordinance%20on%20control%20of%20bureaucrats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20invited%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20the%20AAP.%C2%A0%20The%20party%20said%20Mr%20Singh%20is%20a%20strong%20voice%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20BJP%20would%20have%20put%20him%20in%20jail%20if%20it%20had%20its%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Singh%20raises%20slogans%20and%20the%20entire%20opposition%20unites.%20It%20is%20obvious%20that%20he%20is%20a%20thorn%20in%20the%20government's%20side%20and%20they%20will%20try%20their%20best%20to%20silence%20his%20voice.%20But%20no%20matter%20what%20they%20do%2C%20be%20it%20such%20gimmicks%20or%20the%20misuse%20of%20probe%20agencies%20like%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%2C%20the%20return%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20difficult.%20The%20legal%20wing%20will%20see%20what%20can%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rajya%20Sabha%20proceedings%20resumed%20at%20noon%20after%20being%20adjourned%20for%20an%20hour%2C%20the%20Chairman%20allowed%20the%20question%20hour%20to%20start.%20Many%20opposition%20MPs%20pointed%20out%20that%20they%20had%20submitted%20notices%20under%20Rule%20267%2C%20seeking%20a%20long%20discussion%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20%C2%A0They%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20come%20to%20the%20House%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20and%20initiate%20the%20discussion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20allowed%20the%20question%20hour%20to%20continue.%20When%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Shekhawat%20was%20answering%20questions%20related%20to%20his%20ministry%2C%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%C2%A0%20allegedly%20jumped%20into%20the%20well%20of%20the%20House%20and%20began%20raising%20slogans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20was%20protesting%20against%20the%20question%20hour%20being%20allowed%20to%20go%20on%20when%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20267.%20He%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Chairman%20to%20go%20back%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20agree%20and%20kept%20raising%20slogans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20got%20up%20to%20say%20that%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20discipline%20and%20code%20of%20conduct%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20Chairman%20to%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20Mr%20Singh.%20He%20moved%20a%20motion%20to%20suspend%20him%2C%20which%20was%20adopted%20by%20the%20House%20by%20voice%20vote.%20The%20Chairman%20then%20announced%20Mr%20Singh's%20suspension.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690186080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fti2ukeug_sanjay-singh-rajya-sabha-650_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-sanjay-singh-suspended-from-parliaments-monsoon-session-over-manipur-protest-4235643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20amid%20a%20face-off%20in%20Parliament%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20over%20th