%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fharmanpreet-kaur-should-have-been-careful-with-her-actions-anjum-chopra-101690136449852.html%5C%22%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chopra%20said%20that%20Harmanpreet%20should've%20been%20more%20careful%20with%20the%20choice%20of%20her%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20aggression%20goes%20away%20and%20she%20becomes%20calm%20I'm%20sure%20she%20would%20look%20back%20and%20agree%20that%20she%20needed%20to%20be%20more%20careful%20in%20showing%20her%20disagreement.%20There's%20no%20harm%20in%20voicing%20your%20displeasure%2C%20but%20it's%20how%20and%20when%20you%20do%20it.%20She%20should%20have%20been%20more%20selective%20with%20her%20choice%20of%20words%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20umpiring%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20Chopra%20said%20that%20the%20concerns%20could've%20been%20raised%20in%20a%20better%20way.%20She%20maintained%20that%20Harmanpreet%20should've%20have%20gone%20public%20with%20her%20displeasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20snickometer%20or%20ball-tracking%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20bit%20difficult%20to%20judge.%20But%20if%20they%20(Indian%20team)%20felt%20a%20few%20decisions%20did%20not%20go%20their%20way%2C%20could%20things%20have%20been%20handled%20better%3F%20Why%20did%20it%20come%20down%20to%20the%20Indian%20captain%20going%20to%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20and%20voicing%20her%20displeasure%3F%20It%20could%20have%20been%20communicated%20in%20a%20better%20way.%20How%20did%20the%20situation%20scale%20up%20to%20this%3F%20The%20Indian%20team%20not%20playing%20up%20to%20the%20mark%20can%20be%20a%20cause%20of%20their%20disappointment%20but%20that%20could%20have%20been%20kept%20within%20the%20dressing%20room.%20Going%20out%20in%20public%20like%20this%20(was%20not%20proper)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20also%20put%20the%20blame%20for%20Harmanpreet's%20behaviour%20on%20the%20team's%20performance%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20pleasing%20sight.%20When%20you%20watch%20India-Bangladesh%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20then%20the%20women's%20Ashes%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20you%20could%20see%20the%20stark%20difference.%20One%20of%20the%20basic%20reasons%20is%20the%20pitch.%20The%20moment%20the%20pitch%20is%20true%20you%20can%20expect%20good%20scores%20and%20an%20even%20contest%20between%20bat%20and%20all.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20important%20difference%2C%20though%20I'm%20not%20trying%20to%20say%20that%20is%20the%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20India%20great.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690185720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ft0jdcibg_harmanpreet_650x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgoing-out-in-public-like-this-india-great-slams-harmanpreet-kaur-over-umpiring-rant-4235347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20at%20the%20umpires%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony%20after%20the%20tied%20third%20ODI%20against%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgoing-out-in-public-like-this-india-great-slams-harmanpreet-kaur-over-umpiring-rant-4235347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgoing-out-in-public-like-this-india-great-slams-harmanpreet-kaur-over-umpiring-rant-4235347%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgoing-out-in-public-like-this-india-great-slams-harmanpreet-kaur-over-umpiring-rant-4235347%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20ratifies%208.15%25%20interest%20rate%20on%20Employees%20Provident%20Fund%20for%202022-23%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690185652000%2C%22visual%22%3