%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20how%20it%20passed%20the%20certification%20body's%20filters%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20has%20asked%20for%20the%20scene%20to%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20film.%20Sources%20say%20action%20could%20be%20initiated%20against%20some%20officials%20who%20are%20seen%20as%20responsible%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biopic%20of%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%2C%20the%20mind%20behind%20the%20world's%20first%20atomic%20bomb%2C%20released%20on%20Friday.%20While%20the%20film%20has%20set%20the%20box%20office%20ringing%2C%20the%20controversial%20scene%20in%20the%20Christopher%20Nolan%20epic%20has%20enraged%20some%20Indian%20movie-goers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20is%20perplexed%20as%20to%20how%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20could%20approve%20the%20film%20with%20this%20scene%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Uday%20Mahurkar%2C%20Information%20Commissioner%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20sharing%20a%20press%20release%20by%20the%20'Save%20Culture%20Save%20India%20Foundation'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMOVIE%20OPPENHEIMER'S%20ATTACK%20ON%20BHAGWAD%20GEETA%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPress%20Release%20of%20Save%20Culture%20Save%20India%20Foundation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDate%3A%20July%2022%2C%202023%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20has%20come%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20Save%20Culture%20Save%20India%20Foundation%20that%20the%20movie%20Oppenheimer%20which%20was%20released%20on%2021st%20July%20contains%20scenes%20which%20make%20a%20scathing%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRmJI0q9pXi%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRmJI0q9pXi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Uday%20Mahurkar%20(%40UdayMahurkar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUdayMahurkar%2Fstatus%2F1682763212339695617%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20scene%20in%20the%20film%20shows%20a%20woman%20make%20a%20man%20read%20Bhagwad%20Geeta%20(sic)%20aloud%20while%20getting%20over%20him%20and%20doing%20sexual%20intercourse...%20This%20should%20be%20investigated%20by%20I%20%26amp%3B%20B%20Ministry%20on%20an%20urgent%20basis%20and%20those%20involved%20should%20be%20severely%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20statement%20by%20'Save%20Culture%20Save%20India%20Foundation%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOppenheimer%20is%20the%20first%20film%20directed%20by%20Christopher%20Nolan%20to%20have%20an%20R-rating.%20But%20India's%20censor%20board%20gave%20the%20film%20a%20U%2FA%20rating%20after%20the%20studio%20cut%20some%20shots%20of%20the%20sex%20scene%20to%20reduce%20its%20length.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20cuts%20were%20made%20by%20the%20studio%20themselves%20because%20they%20did%20not%20think%20the%20censor%20board%20would%20allow%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690184880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F2d57t44s_oppenheimer_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foppenheimer-sex-scene-oppenheimer-bhagavad-gita-scene-anurag-thakur-upset-at-objectionable-seen-in-oppenheimer-minister-pulls-up-film-certification-bo-4235672%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Anurag%20Thakur%20today%20pulled%20up%20the%20film%20certification%20body%2C%20popularly%20called%20the%20censor%20board%2C%20over%20'objectionable'%20scenes%20in%20'Oppenheimer'%20film%20which%20released%20in%20India%20last%20weekend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foppenheimer-sex-scene-oppenheimer-bhagavad-gita-scene-anurag-thakur-upset-at-objectionable-seen-in-oppenheimer-minister-pulls-up-film-certification-bo-4235672%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foppenheimer-sex-scene-oppenheimer-bhagavad-gi