nt%20of%20police%2C%20Saharanpur%20on%20July%2014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fnorth-and-central%2Fncpcr-seeks-action-against-darul-uloom-deobands-book-legitimising-sex-with-minors-1239954.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20material%20should%20be%20blocked%20under%20section%2069A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%20which%20allows%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20ask%20any%20of%20its%20agencies%20or%20an%20intermediary%20to%20block%20public%20access%20to%20any%20information%20generated%20stored%20on%20any%20computer%20resource.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20child%20rights%20body%20has%20asked%20for%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20the%20books%20prescribed%20in%20the%20syllabus%20and%20an%20%E2%80%98action%20taken%E2%80%99%20report%20from%20the%20district%20administration%20in%20four%20days.%20This%20is%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20second%20complaint%20since%20January%20last%20year%20when%20it%20had%20written%20to%20the%20administration%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20several%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Efatwas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20Darul%20Uloom%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENCPCR%20chief%20Priyank%20Kanoongo%20said%20that%20the%20book%20legitimises%20sexual%20relations%20with%20minors.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20minors%2C%20we%20mean%20girls%20who%20are%20yet%20to%20reach%20puberty.%20There%20are%20passages%20that%20say%20that%20men%20do%20not%20have%20to%20bathe%20after%20such%20an%20act%20to%20read%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enamaz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20are%20several%20such%20references%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kanungo%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20chapter%20in%20the%20NCERT-prescribed%20English%20textbook%20for%20Class%2011th%20on%20child%20marriage%20and%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20minor%20has%20gone%20under%20the%20NCPCR%E2%80%99s%20radar.%20The%20chapter%2C%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERanga%E2%80%99s%20Marriage%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20about%20a%20man%20in%20his%20mid-twenties%20who%20marries%20an%2011-year-old%20and%20has%20two%20children%20with%20her%20before%20she%20turns%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20opposition%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20has%20criticised%20the%20NCPCR%20for%20pushing%20a%20soft%20Hindutva%20agenda%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fground-reports%2Fncpcr-has-a-new-mojo-and-mission-aap-madrasas-byjus-nothing-is-off-limits%2F1647621%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Kanoongo%20has%20also%20been%20called%20out%20for%20turning%20the%20NCPCR%E2%80%99s%20focus%20away%20from%20ensuring%20child%20rights%20and%20meddling%20in%20political%20warfare%20that%20is%20outside%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20purview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690183363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24124346%2FDarul_Uloom_Deoband.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fncpcr-seeks-removal-of-controversial-book-from-darul-uloom-deobands-curriculum%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20child%20rights%20body%20has%20said%20that%20Maulana%20Ashraf%20Ali%20Thanvi's%20book%C2%A0Bahishti%20Zewar%C2%A0legitimises%20sexual%20relations%20with%20minors%20and%20should%20be%20blocked%20under%20section%2069A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fncpcr-seeks-removal-of-controversial-book-from-darul-uloom-deobands-curriculum%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Come%20on%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20X%20logo%20isn