n%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20bills%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration%20and%20passing%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Multi-State%20Co-operative%20Societies%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20It%20will%20be%20tabled%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20seeks%20to%20amend%20the%20Multi-State%20Co-operative%20Societies%20Act%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSCS%20(Amendment)%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%207%20last%20year.%20It%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20of%20both%20the%20Houses%20on%20December%2020%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20bill%20will%20strengthen%20accountability%20in%20cooperative%20societies%20and%20reform%20their%20electoral%20process%20by%20improving%20the%20monitoring%20mechanism%20and%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20in%20state%20cooperatives.%20The%20bill%20will%20also%20allow%20state%20cooperative%20societies%20to%20merge%20into%20an%20existing%20multi-state%20cooperative%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20important%20provisions%20entails%20that%20a%20prior%20government%20permission%20will%20be%20required%20for%20multi-state%20co-operative%20societies%20for%20the%20redemption%20of%20their%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20opposition%20parties%20are%20opposed%20to%20it%20saying%20they%20won't%20allow%20central%20interference%20in%20the%20working%20of%20cooperatives%20as%20it%20is%20a%20state%20subject%20and%20many%20of%20the%20bill's%20provisions%20go%20against%20the%20autonomy%20enjoyed%20by%20these%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20bill%20expected%20to%20be%20tabled%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20It%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20discussed%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20budget%20session%20but%20was%20deferred.%20The%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20on%20December%2016%2C%202021%20by%20Bhupender%20Yadav%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20environment%2C%20forest%20and%20climate%20change%20and%20seeks%20to%20amend%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20legislation%20seeks%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20wild%20medicinal%20plants%20and%20encourage%20their%20cultivation.%20It%20is%20aimed%20at%20encouraging%20Indian%20system%20of%20medicine%20and%20facilitate%20an%20environment%20for%20collaborative%20research%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20also%20seeks%20to%20exempt%20those%20making%20medicinal%20products%20from%20taking%20permission%20from%20the%20National%20Biodiversity%20Authority%20(NBA)%20and%20decriminalise%20violation%20and%20withdraw%20power%20given%20to%20it%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20a%20defaulting%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20joint%20committee%20on%20December%2020%2C%202021%20due%20to%20concerns%20that%20the%20amendments%20contradicted%20the%20spirit%20of%20Convention%20on%20Biological%20Diversity%20(CBD).%20%C2%A0The%20panel%20submitted%20its%20report%20in%20Parliament%20on%20August%202%2C%202022%2C%20recommending%20that%20the%20bill%20may%20be%20passed%20after%20the%20inclusion%20of%20their%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20rejected%20the%20amendments%20saying%20it%20favours%20trade%20and%20business%20over%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20important%20bill%20ready%20for%20consideration%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20National%20Nursing%20and%20Midwifery%20Commission%20Bill%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20It%20seeks%20to%20a%20new%20commission%20that%20will%20frame%20policies%2C%20regulate%20standards%20of%20nursing%20and%20midwifery%20education%20and%20frame%20regulation%20for%20their%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20proposes%20to%20provide%20uniform%20entry%20and%20exit%20examinations%2C%20monitor%20professional%20ethics%20and%20control%20state%20commissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20commission%20will%20be%20appointed%20by%20central%20and%20state%20ministries%2C%20and%20a%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20at%20least%20once%20every%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Constitution%20(Scheduled%20Castes)%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20tabled%20today%20by%20Minister%20of%20Tribal%20Affairs%20Arjun%20Munda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20already%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20talks%20about%20including%20certain%20communities%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list.%20The%20minister%20could%20also%20move%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EConstitution%20(Scheduled%20Tribes)%20Order%20(Third%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20on%20the%20ST%20list%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690182840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Frtvrrj68_parliament-generic-pti_625x300_23_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-bills-expected-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-and-their-significance-4235679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%2C%20Union%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20had%20said%20that%2031%20bills%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20Parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-bills-expected-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-and-their-significance-4235679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-bills-expected-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-and-their-significance-4235679%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-bills-expected-to-be-tabled-in-parliament-today-and-their-significance-4235679%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raigad%3