20leaves%20behind%20germs%20of%20rot%20which%20we%20must%20clinically%20detect%20and%20remove%20from%20our%20land%20and%20from%20our%20minds%20as%20well%26quot%3B.%20Fanon%20proposes%20that%20the%20residual%20effects%20of%20colonialism%20are%20not%20simply%20confined%20to%20the%20visible%2C%20tangible%20aspects%20of%20political%20or%20economic%20structures%20but%20are%20embedded%20deeply%20within%20the%20psyche%20of%20the%20colonised%2C%20affecting%20their%20identity%20and%20cultural%20expression.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20not%20only%20a%20political%20imperative%20but%20also%20a%20psychological%20and%20cultural%20necessity%20to%20discard%20the%20colonial%20legacy%20in%20order%20to%20foster%20a%20genuinely%20independent%20and%20self-determined%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20Commonwealth.%20Despite%20being%20viewed%20by%20some%20as%20a%20benign%20institution%20promoting%20shared%20values%20and%20cooperation%20among%20member%20nations%2C%20its%20roots%20in%20British%20colonialism%20are%20undeniable.%20In%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20Commonwealth%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20maintain%20ties%20with%20former%20British%20colonies%20and%20retain%20some%20influence%20over%20them.%20For%20nations%20still%20part%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%2C%20it%20can%20be%20argued%20that%20this%20continues%20a%20colonial%20legacy.%20Being%20part%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%20can%20inadvertently%20perpetuate%20the%20very%20colonial%20ties%20that%20nations%20seek%20to%20transcend%2C%20muddling%20the%20path%20to%20genuine%20post-colonial%20identity%20and%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20nations%20like%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20embraced%20the%20Commonwealth%20immediately%20upon%20decolonization%2C%20India%2C%20with%20its%20long%20and%20tumultuous%20history%20of%20colonization%2C%20exhibited%20an%20unexpected%20and%20arguably%20misplaced%20allegiance.%20India's%20decision%20to%20remain%20within%20the%20Commonwealth%20after%20gaining%20dominion%20status%20in%201947%20and%20becoming%20a%20republic%20in%201950%2C%20post%20the%201949%20London%20Declaration%2C%20remains%20a%20perplexing%20diplomatic%20conundrum.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20India%20should%20have%20been%20relentlessly%20asserting%20its%20newfound%20independence%20and%20sovereignty%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%20it%20ironically%20chose%20to%20retain%20symbolic%20ties%20with%20the%20very%20colonial%20power%20it%20had%20fought%20so%20ardently%20against.%20Under%20the%20London%20Declaration%2C%20India%20accepted%20the%20King%20as%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20free%20association%20of%20its%20independent%20member%20nations%20and%2C%20as%20such%2C%20the%20Head%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%20(until%20India%20adopted%20its%20constitution).%20The%20acceptance%20of%20King%20George%20VI%20as%20a%20symbolic%20head%2C%20even%20if%20just%20in%20title%2C%20seemed%20to%20undermine%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20hard-won%20independence.%20The%20nation%20had%20just%20rid%20itself%20of%20the%20monarchy%3B%20to%20tacitly%20endorse%20a%20monarchical%20figurehead%20in%20any%20capacity%20was%20contradictory%20and%20almost%20self-deprecating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20beckons%20the%20question%3A%20Why%20did%20India%2C%20after%20embarking%20on%20a%20path%20of%20self-governance%20and%20republicanism%2C%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20linger%20in%20the%20shadows%20of%20its%20colonial%20past%3F%20In%20this%20particular%20instance%2C%20the%20nation's%20leadership%20could%20be%20criticized%20for%20not%20taking%20a%20more%20assertive%20stand%20that%20resonated%20with%20its%20aspirations%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20its%20freedom%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201949%2C%20India's%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20Commonwealth%20may%20have%20seemed%20like%20a%20pragmatic%20move%3B%20tethered%20as%20it%20was%20to%20England's%20supply%20of%20defence%20materials%20and%20the%20financial%20incentives%20of%20foreign%20exchange%20and%20customs%20exemptions.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20offered%20a%20stage%20to%20rebuff%20Pakistan's%20disparaging%20narratives.%20However%2C%20in%20hindsight%2C%20relying%20on%20such%20vestiges%20of%20colonial%20dependency%20for%20defence%2C%20economic%20favours%2C%20or%20diplomatic%20clout%20feels%20like%20an%20anachronistic%20misstep.%20Such%20motivations%20are%20clearly%20outdated%20and%20redundant%20in%20our%20contemporary%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commonwealth%20has%20been%20critiqued%20as%20an%20assemblage%20of%20nations%20bearing%20a%20colonial%20legacy%2C%20leading%20to%20debates%20about%20the%20relevance%20of%20India's%20membership%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%20Given%20India's%20stature%20and%20its%20colonial%20history%2C%20questions%20arise%20concerning%20the%20necessity%20of%20India's%20continued%20membership%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20light%20of%20perceived%20discrepancies%20in%20treatment%20despite%20being%20the%20largest%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20India's%20status%20quo%20approach%20to%20its%20membership%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%20has%20presented%20a%20disquieting%20inertia%20in%20its%20foreign%20policy.%20Despite%20having%20evolved%20into%20a%20global%20power%20with%20its%20own%20unique%20geostrategic%20interests%20and%20initiatives%2C%20the%20country%20inexplicably%20clings%20to%20a%20vestige%20of%20its%20colonial%20past.%20There%20is%20an%20undeniable%20paucity%20of%20substantive%20benefits%20that%20India%20garners%20from%20the%20Commonwealth.%20While%20the%20nation%20often%20excels%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20one%20must%20question%20if%20the%20occasional%20sports%20accolades%20truly%20justify%20the%20perpetuation%20of%20such%20an%20incongruous%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20though%20a%20platform%20for%20showcasing%20talent%20and%20fostering%20sportsmanship%2C%20cannot%20be%20the%20sole%20rationale%20for%20maintaining%20India's%20membership%20of%20the%20Commonwealth.%20Is%20it%20not%20perplexing%20that%20a%20nation%20that%20has%20surmounted%20numerous%20challenges%20and%20reached%20significant%20milestones%20in%20various%20fields%20should%20attach%20such%20considerable%20significance%20to%20a%20mere%20sporting%20event%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20Commonwealth's%20relative%20insignificance%20in%20contemporary%20geopolitics%20and%20its%20minimal%20influence%20in%20resolving%20global%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20poverty%2C%20and%20regional%20conflicts%2C%20places%20the%20credibility%20and%20relevance%20of%20India's%20continued%20membership%20under%20rigorous%20scrutiny.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20India%20is%20shackled%20to%20an%20antiquated%20relic%20of%20a%20bygone%20era%2C%20one%20that%20only%20serves%20as%20a%20grim%20reminder%20of%20its%20colonial%20past%20rather%20than%20contributing%20constructively%20to%20its%20present%20and%20future%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20time%20has%20come%20for%20India%20to%20reassess%20and%20recalibrate%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20Commonwealth.%20It%20must%20ascertain%20whether%20this%20colonial%20artefact%20warrants%20preservation%20or%20if%20it%20is%20indeed%20an%20obsolete%20association%20that%20only%20perpetuates%20a%20historical%20anomaly%20far%20removed%20from%20India's%20progressive%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690182420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F6lojvtco_commonwealth-logo-_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-incongruous-commonwealth-affiliation-4235610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20need%20to%20break%20free%20of%20the%20shackles%20of%20colonial%20legacy%20is%20an%20essential%20step%20for%20former%20colonies%20to%20assert%20their%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-incongruous-commonwealth-affiliation-4235610%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-incongruous-commonwealth-affiliation-4235610%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-incongruous-commonwealth-affiliation-4235610%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Not%20A%20Brick%20Removed...%2C%5C%22%20Supreme%20Court%20Told%20As%20Gyanvapi%20Survey%20Begins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20put%20on%20hold%20for%20two%20days%20the%20survey%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20at%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque's%20management%20committee%20had%20approached%20the%20centre%20with%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20survey%20may%20lead%20to%20excavation%20at%20the%20historic%20mosque%20complex%20that%20is%20located%20right%20next%20to%20the%20iconic%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20at%20Varanasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%2C%20however%2C%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20the%20survey%20will%20in%20no%20way%20alter%20the%20structure%20and%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20brick%20has%20been%20removed%20nor%20is%20it%20planned%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20survey%20plan%20includes%20only%20measurement%2C%20photography%20and%20radar%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20ASI%20is%20not%20contemplating%20carrying%20out%20any%20excavation%20in%20pursuance%20of%20the%20order.%20We%20record%20the%20statement%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20no%20excavation%20at%20the%20site%20is%20contemplated%20at%20this%20stage%20for%20a%20period%20of%20one%20week%20until%20next%20week%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20taking%20the%20centre's%20submissions%20on%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20hit%20headlines%20in%202021%20after%20a%20group%20of%20Hindu%20women%20approached%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20court%20for%20permission%20to%20worship%20deities%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lower%20court%20then%20ordered%20a%20video%20survey%20of%20the%20complex%20during%20which%20an%20object%20was%20discovered%20that%20a%20section%20of%20people%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20shivling.%20The%20mosque%20management%20committee%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20fountain%20in%20the%20wazookhana%20(pool)%20to%20wash%20hands%20and%20feet%20before%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20issue%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20sealed%20off%20the%20pool%20(wazookhana).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20petition%20that%20challenge%20the%20maintainability%20of%20the%20request%20to%20worship%20Hindu%20deities%20found%20inside%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20a%20Varanasi%20court's%20ruling%2C%20allowing%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20ASI%20inside%20the%20mosque%20complex%20except%20the%20pool%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20expressing%20concerns%20regarding%20excavation%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20now%20allowed%20the%20petitioners%20to%20approach%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20order%20for%20the%20ASI%20survey%20and%20asked%20the%20high%20court's%20registrar%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20placed%20before%20a%20bench%20before%20the%20status%20quo%20order%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690182120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht