ntent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20and%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20at%20each%20other's%20throats%20again%20over%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-women-video-manipur-violence-latest-proof-of-state-complicity-manipur-bjp-mla-paolienlal-haokip-claims-ethnic-violence-was-avoidable-4234147%5C%22%3Ethe%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20Opposition%20MPs%20have%2C%20for%20three%20consecutive%20working%20days%20now%2C%20submitted%20strongly-worded%20adjournment%20notices%20in%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20while%20BJP%20MPs%20from%20Rajasthan%20gathered%20near%20the%20Gandhi%20statue%20in%20the%20Parliament%20House%20premises%20over%20allegations%20of%20growing%20atrocities%20against%20women%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20demanded%20immediate%20dismissal%20of%20the%20state%20government%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%C2%A0MPs%20from%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%20also%20gathered%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20statue%2C%20demanding%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20speak%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20and%20also%20suspend%20the%20N%20Biren%20Singh-led%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20said%20he%20has%20received%2011%20notices%20for%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20176%2C%20and%C2%A027%20under%20Rule%20267%20today.%20BJP%20MPs%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20and%20Sushil%20Modi%20have%20given%20notices%20to%20raise%20discussion%20on%20violence%20during%20the%20Panchayat%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20upper%20house%20has%20been%20adjourned%20till%202%20pm%20amid%20loud%20protests.%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20suspended%20by%20the%20Chairman%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20for%20allegedly%20disrupting%20house%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%2C%20who%20hasn't%20allowed%20any%20motion%20under%20Rule%20267%20during%20his%20term%20so%20far%2C%20last%20year%20said%20motions%20moved%20under%20the%20rule%20%26quot%3Bhave%20become%20a%20known%20mechanism%20of%20causing%20disruption%26quot%3B.%20The%20Opposition%20is%20demanding%20that%20MPs%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20issue%20without%20any%20time-limit%2C%20for%20which%20all%20other%20business%20should%20be%20suspended%20for%20the%20day%20--%20which%20Rule%20267%20of%20the%20house%20allows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERule%20176%2C%20which%20the%20Centre%20is%20insistent%20on%2C%20allows%20for%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%2C%20not%20exceeding%20two-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20on%20a%20particular%20issue.%20It%20states%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20member%20desirous%20of%20raising%20discussion%20on%20a%20matter%20of%20urgent%20public%20importance%20may%20give%20notice%20in%20writing%20to%20the%20Secretary-General%20specifying%20clearly%20and%20precisely%20the%20matter%20to%20be%20raised%3A%20Provided%20that%20the%20notice%20shall%20be%20accompanied%20by%20an%20explanatory%20note%20stating%20reasons%20for%20raising%20discussion%20on%20the%20matter%20in%20question%3A%20Provided%20further%20that%20the%20notice%20shall%20be%20supported%20by%20the%20signatures%20of%20at%20least%20two%20other%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Rule%20176%2C%20the%20matter%20can%20be%20taken%20up%20immediately%2C%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20or%20even%20the%20next%20day.%20The%20rule%2C%20however%2C%20is%20clear%20that%20no%20formal%20motion%20or%20voting%20shall%20be%20held%20under%20a%20short-duration%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20debate%20in%20the%20House%20under%20Rule%20267%2C%20but%20some%20ministers%20of%20Modi%20government%20say%20there%20will%20be%20only%20a%20short%20duration%20discussion%2C%20others%20says%20that%20there%20will%20only%20be%20a%20half%20an%20hour%20discussion.%20Rule%20267%20debate%20can%20go%20on%20for%20hours%2C%20voting%20can%20also%20happ