Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwill-salman-khans-tiger-3-trailer-be-attached-to-shah-rukh-khans-jawan-heres-what-we-know%2Farticleshow%2F102069519.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20In%20The%20Name%20Of%20I.N.D.I.A%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBrinda%20Karat%2C%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20the%20much%20talked%20about%20Bengaluru%20meeting%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20strongly%20criticised%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20as%20anti-democratic.%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20openly%20expressed%20his%20reluctance%20to%20be%20the%20Convenor%20of%20the%20yet-to-be-born%20coalition.%20Also%2C%20he%20appears%20discomfited%20by%20the%20way%20things%20are%20being%20handled%20by%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20or%20INDIA%2C%20a%20nice%20acronym%20selected%20by%20the%20opposition's%20dream%20coalition%2C%20can't%20hide%20the%20deep-seated%20acrimony%20within%2C%20and%20the%20contradictions%20in%20this%20grouping.%20What%20clearly%20emerges%20is%20that%20the%20constituents'%20daydreams%20of%20a%20repeat%20of%202004%20have%20no%20ground%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20five%20key%20factors%20clearly%20underscore%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20distance%20between%202004%20and%202024%20is%20not%20just%2020%20years.%20It%20is%20so%20much%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20was%20a%20coalition%20of%2022%20parties%2C%20whereas%20the%20BJP%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20although%20an%20NDA%20government%2C%20has%20a%20clear%20majority%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too%2C%20it%20is%20comfortably%20placed.%20Naturally%2C%20when%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20others%20refused%20to%20do%20business%20with%20the%20BJP%20prior%20to%202004%2C%20there%20was%20the%20lurking%20danger%20of%20electoral%20roadblocks.%20In%20contrast%2C%20political%20parties%20that%20had%20deserted%20the%20NDA%20of%20their%20own%20volition%20between%202018%20and%202023%2C%20are%20limping%20back%20to%20the%20NDA.%20This%20includes%20the%20officially%20recognised%20Shiv%20Sena%20of%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20compared%20to%202004%2C%20the%20internal%20contradictions%20within%20the%20opposition%20coalition%20that%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20shape%20are%20potential%20obstacles%20to%20their%20coming%20together.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20versus%20Congress%20(Punjab)%2C%20Trinamool%20versus%20Left%20(%20West%20Bengal)%2C%20and%20Left%20versus%20Congress%20(Kerala)%20are%20some%20of%20the%20glaring%20fault%20lines.%20Many%20key%20questions%20like%20whether%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20would%20support%20quota%20for%20Muslims%2C%20as%20fondly%20envisioned%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20also%20remain%20unanswered.%20Ironing%20out%20these%20contradictions%20is%20supremely%20important%20as%2C%20unlike%202004%2C%20people%20have%20seen%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20BJP's%20clear%20governance%20vision%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Comparable%20data%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20With%20its%20record%20of%20failures%20in%20dealing%20with%20poverty%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20development%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20Congress's%20attempt%20to%20build%20a%20narrative%20around%20guarantees%20fails%20to%20cut%20much%20ice%20with%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20in%20many%20edits%2C%20this%20INDIA%20coalition%20cannot%20be%20woven%20around%20just%20an%20anti-PM%20Modi%20theme.%20%C2%A0Even%20in%202004%2C%20the%20verdict%20was%20not%20against%20PM%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%20Also%2C%20compared%20to%20Atal%20ji%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20successfully%20governed%20for%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time%2C%20enabling%20him%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20practically%20every%20sphere%20of%20public%20life.%20Vajpayee's%20narrative%20of%20Good%20Governance%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20a%20different%20level%20by%20PM%20Modi.%20Through%20his%20hugely%20influential%20presence%20on%20social%20media%2C%20innovative%20ways%20of%20communicating%20with%20the%20people%20and%20push%20for%20technology%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20earned%20a%20place%20in%20the%20ethos%20of%20the%20aspirational%20Gen-Next%20Indians%2C%20and%20that%20is%20something%20unique%20about%20him.%20Even%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20though%20much%20younger%20than%20Modi%20during%20his%20Prime%20Ministership%2C%20could%20not%20manage%20that%20connection%20with%20the%20younger%20generation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourthly%2C%20and%20perhaps%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20new%20alliance's%20claim%20of%20being%20Developmental%20and%20Inclusive%2C%20as%20the%20title%20suggests%2C%20is%20far%20from%20facts.%20The%20imagination%20of%20those%20who%20led%20India's%20Grand%20Old%20Party%2C%20the%20Congress%20-%20the%20only%20party%20that%20has%20ruled%20this%20country%20for%20over%20six%20decades%20-%20did%20not%20and%20could%20not%20go%20beyond%20'most%20backward%20districts'%2C%20the%20nomenclature%20that%20Modi%20changed%20to%20aspirational%20districts.%20It%20was%20Vajpayee%2C%20not%20the%20Congress%2C%20who%20created%20the%20Department%20of%20the%20North%20East%20region%2C%20a%20testimony%20to%20the%20BJP's%20developmental-inclusive%20approach.%20Again%2C%20it%20was%20Vajpayee%20who%20carved%20out%20a%20separate%20Ministry%20for%20Tribal%20Welfare%20and%20changed%20the%20condescending%20term%20Social%20Welfare%20into%20a%20more%20egalitarian%20Social%20Justice.%20Yet%20those%20who%20made%20a%20Brouhaha%20in%20Bengaluru%20have%20the%20gumption%20of%20claiming%20to%20be%20Developmental%20and%20Inclusive.%20The%20Congress%20must%20answer%20-%20if%20they%20are%20serious%20about%20the%20claim%2C%20why%20did%20they%20deny%20quota%20to%20the%20underprivileged%20communities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20hiding%20behind%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20370%3F%20Why%20were%20economically%20backward%20sections%20denied%20quota%20prior%20to%20the%20Modi%20regime%3F%20Why%20didn't%20they%20think%20of%20promoting%20education%20in%20the%20mother%20tongue%20to%20boost%20regional%20languages%20in%20India%3F%20Why%20was%20the%20need%20for%20building%20a%20network%20of%20rail%2C%20road%20and%20air%20travel%20to%20facilitate%20access%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20our%20country%20ignored%20all%20along%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20those%20who%20gathered%20at%20Bengaluru%20must%20know%20that%20as%20far%20as%20development%20politics%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20credibility%20of%20PM%20Modi%20is%20unparalleled.%20Even%20if%20one%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20collective%20value%20of%20the%20performances%20of%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20Siddaramaiya%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20PM%20Modi%20stands%20head%20and%20shoulders%20above%20all%20of%20them.%20Genuine%20concern%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20underprivileged%2C%20creative%20solutions%20to%20chronic%20governance%20issues%2C%20out-of-the%20box%20thinking%20to%20ensure%20results%20and%20the%20art%20of%20implementation%20are%20the%20key%20features%20of%20the%20Modi%20brand%20of%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20governance%20is%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20complex%20by%20the%20day.%20It%20takes%20an%20unusually%20high%20level%20of%20ability%20to%20govern%20and%20strike%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20being%20popular%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20popular%20interest%20with%20a%20long-term%20vision.%20In%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20educating%20people%20all%20the%20time%20with%20every%20element%20of%20honesty%2C%20integrity%20and%20credibility%20at%20one's%20command%20remains%20the%20only%20way.%20PM%20Modi's%20emphasis%20on%20people's%20participation%20in%20all%20development%20initiatives%3B%20his%20avowed%20commitment%20to%20taking%20decisions%20that%20may%20not%20be%20popular%20but%20are%20unquestionably%20%C2%A0in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%3B%20his%20insistence%20on%20evolving%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20diverse%20manifestations%20of%20our%20innate%20unity%20through%20programmes%20like%20Ek%20Bharat%2C%20Sreshtha%20Bharat%3B%20his%20passionate%20appeal%20to%20parents%20of%20young%20boys%20and%20girls%20to%20make%20both%20genders%20equally%20answerable%20for%20their%20personal%20conduct%20are%20examples%20of%20his%20efforts%20towards%20public%20education.%20Against%20this%2C%20the%20partners%20of%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20have%20precious%20little%20to%20show%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20any%20resolve%20to%20educate%20people%20on%20issues%20apparently%20not%20so%20popular%20and%20yet%20serving%20the%20larger%20interests%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20coalition%20remains%20a%20feeble%20attempt%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20nationalistic%20fervour%20and%20aspirational%20ethos%20painstakingly%20crafted%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Not%20just%20'Millennials'%2C%20even%20common%20voters%20today%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20hoodwinked%20by%20slogan-mongering.%20With%20little%20evidence%2C%20INDIA's%20claim%20of%20being%20Nationalist%2C%20Developmental%20and%20Inclusive%20falls%20absolutely%20flat.%20What%20remains%20then%20is%20'India'%20and%20'Alliance'%2C%20which%20is%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20those%20who%20desperately%20need%20mutual%20support%20to%20present%20their%20case%20nationally.%20The%20story%20of%20this%20alliance%20is%20nothing%20but%20%26quot%3Byou%20scratch%20my%20back%20and...'.%20Worse%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20mutual%20back-stabbing%20in%20the%20name%20of%20mutual%20back-scratching%20is%20very%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVinay%20Sahasrabuddhe%20is%20former%20MP%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20columnist%2C%20besides%20being%20President%20of%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Cultural%20Relations%20(ICCR)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3