0by%20a%20suspect%20who%20robbed%20him%20of%20his%20vehicle%20and%20fled%20the%20scene%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20witnesses%20came%20to%20his%20aid%20and%20called%20for%20help%20before%20Nath%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20trauma%20centre%20where%20he%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20on%20July%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddhartha%20Nath%2C%20Consul%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Toronto%2C%20said%20Nath's%20death%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bheartrending%20loss%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20extended%20his%20condolences%20to%20family%20members%2C%20friends%20and%20the%20wider%20community%2C%20the%20CBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20consulate%20general%20has%20contacted%20the%20family%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20heartening%20for%20me%20to%20see%20how%20the%20community%20responded%2C%20came%20together%20both%20online%20and%20physically%20to%20support%20the%20family%20in%20this%20time%20of%20grief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Consul%20General%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20nothing%20can%20make%20good%20the%20loss%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20some%20solace%20to%20the%20grieving%20family%20and%20it's%20also%20a%20signal%20of%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20community%20because%20it%20is%20in%20times%20like%20this%20when%20the%20spirit%20and%20the%20solidarity%20and%20the%20sense%20of%20empathy%20is%20tested.%26quot%3B%20The%20Consul%20General%20said%20he%20hopes%20the%20people%20responsible%20are%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20King%20said%20despite%20the%20infancy%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20police%20believe%20Nath%20was%20an%20innocent%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENath's%20vehicle%20was%20found%20abandoned%20in%20the%20hours%20following%20the%20attack%20in%20the%20area%20of%20Old%20Creditview%20and%20Old%20Derry%20roads%20--%20less%20than%20five%20kilometres%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20King%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20working%20theory%20is%20that%20perhaps%20there%20may%20have%20been%20extensive%20injuries%20(to%20Nath)%20that%20may%20not%20have%20been%20anticipated%20and%20that%20may%20have%20caused%20(the%20suspects)%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20vehicle%20early%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20has%20since%20been%20forensically%20examined%20and%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%E2%80%9D%20pieces%20of%20evidence%20have%20been%20retrieved%2C%20King%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20say%20there%20is%20no%20known%20connection%20between%20Nath%20and%20his%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20remind%20those%20involved%20that%20regardless%20of%20your%20level%20of%20participation%2C%20you%20are%20complicit%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Gurvinder%20Nath%20and%20you%20will%20be%20arrested%20and%20charged%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20King%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENath's%20body%20will%20be%20flown%20to%20India%20on%20July%2027%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Toronto%2C%20Canadian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20(CBC)%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20CTV%20News%20Toronto%20spoke%20to%20family%20and%20friends%20of%20Nath%2C%20who%20said%20the%20Brampton%20resident%20was%20on%20summer%20break%20before%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20final%20semester%20of%20business%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20innocent%2C%20he%20was%20just%20delivering%20pizza%20%5Bwhen%5D%20random%20people%20hit%20him%20on%20his%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nath's%20cousin%2C%20Balram%20Krishan%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENath%20arrived%20in%20Canada%20from%20India%20in%20July%20of%202021%20and%20had%20plans%20to%20open%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20more%20than%20200%20people%20gathered%20in%20Mississauga%20at%20a%20candlelight%20vigil%20for%20Nath%2C%20the%20CBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeakers%20at%20the%20vigil%20said%20that%20Nath%20came%20to%20Canada%20carrying%20his%20family's%20hopes%20and%20now%20his%2