r%20losing%20their%20blue%20badge.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwitter%20then%20introduced%20gold%20and%20silver%20ticks%20for%20brands%20and%20government%20figures%2C%20respectively.%20In%20one%20of%20its%20many%20U-turns%2C%20the%20microblogging%20site%20earlier%20this%20year%20started%20rolling%20out%20blue%20ticks%20again%2C%20to%20celebrities%20using%20the%20platform%20to%20endorse%20that%20they%20are%20not%20fakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnother%20move%20by%20Musk%20that%20sparked%20outrage%20was%20his%20decision%20to%20reinstate%20many%20high-profile%20accounts%20suspended%20by%20the%20previous%20Twitter%20leadership.%20Among%20them%20were%20Ye%20(rapper%20Kanye%20West)%2C%20accused%20of%20sharing%20antisemitic%20posts%2C%20influencer%20Andrew%20Tate%2C%20now%20in%20a%20Romania%20prison%20on%20charges%20of%20human%20trafficking%2C%20and%20former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20accused%20of%20instigating%20Capitol%20Hill%20riots.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMusk%20also%20drew%20heavy%20criticism%20for%20mass%20layoffs%20at%20Twitter%20shortly%20after%20the%20takeover.%20Nearly%20half%20of%20its%20workforce%20were%20laid%20off%20in%20a%20cost-cutting%20measure.%20The%20Twitter%20boss%20also%20issued%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20employees%20in%20a%20mail%20that%20said%20employees%20will%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20be%20extremely%20hardcore%20and%20that%20only%20exceptional%20performance%20will%20constitute%20a%20passing%20grade%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmid%20the%20big%20changes%20on%20the%20platforms%20and%20inside%20its%20offices%2C%20Twitter's%20advertising%20business%20partially%20collapsed.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Musk%20admitted%20that%20Twitter%20had%20seen%20a%20nearly%2050%20per%20cent%20drop%20in%20ad%20revenue.%20The%20microblogging%20site%20was%20facing%20troubles%20even%20before%20the%20takeover%2C%20and%20its%20influence%20was%20popularity%20were%20not%20translating%20into%20profit.%20Twitter's%20cash%20flow%20remains%20negative%20because%20of%20the%20drop%20in%20ad%20revenue%20and%20heavy%20debt%20load%2C%20Musk%20has%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20search%20for%20new%20ways%20of%20generating%20revenue%2C%20Musk%20has%20moved%20to%20introducing%20payments%20and%20commerce%20through%20the%20platform.%20Musk%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20Twitter%20to%20offer%20services%20such%20as%20peer-to-peer%20transactions%20as%20part%20of%20his%20vision%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20app%26quot%3B%20that%20functions%20as%20a%20social%20media%20platform%20as%20well%20as%20facilitate%20payments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERough%20estimates%20put%20Twitter's%20daily%20active%20users%20count%20at%20nearly%20200%20million.%20The%20site%20has%2C%20however%2C%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20technical%20snags%20since%20the%20takeover%20as%20Musk%20fine-tuned%20the%20platform.%20Among%20these%20changes%20are%20the%20%26quot%3BFor%20You%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFollowing%26quot%3B%20tabs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwitter%20is%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20facing%20competition.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Facebook%20parent%20Meta%20launched%20a%20text-based%20platform%2C%20Threads.%20The%20new%20platform%20linked%20to%20Instagram%20has%20already%20clocked%20about%20150%20million%20users%2C%20according%20to%20estimates.%20However%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20users%20spend%20on%20Threads%20has%20plummeted%20since%20its%20launch%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20market%20analysis%20firm%20Sensor%20Tower%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20Musk%20moves%20to%20change%20Twitter's%20name%20and%20logo%2C%20many%20influencers%20have%20announced%20that%20they%20will%20quit%20the%20platform.%20This%20is%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20people%20exiting%20the%20platform%20after%20an%20exodus%20that%20followed%20Musk's%20takeover.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMusk%20has%20already%20named%20Twitter's%20parent%20company%20the%20X%20Corporation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20good%20enough%20X%20logo%20is%20posted%20tonight%2C%20we'll%20make%20(it)%2