20Global%20Prime%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23153053%2FUntitled-design-7-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Espoken%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20self-important%20legislators%2C%20who%20for%20some%20reason%20believe%20themselves%20to%20be%20essential%20features%20of%20democracy%2C%20demanded%20that%20he%20speak%20on%20Manipur%20in%20parliament%2C%20they%20yet%20again%20showed%20their%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20how%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20chief%20executive%20non-pareil%2C%20has%20transformed%20the%20character%20of%20prime%20ministerial%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20lesser%20prime%20ministers%20who%20slavishly%20toed%20the%20straight%20and%20narrow%20thought%20themselves%20accountable%20to%20parliament%2C%20our%20kingly%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20recognises%20only%20the%20adoring%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20praja%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20their%20pettifogging%20representatives%2C%20or%20the%20institution%20which%20they%20use%20to%20float%20anti-national%20and%20anti-kingly%20queries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhich%20is%20why%20he%20took%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnation%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20scruff%20of%20its%20obedient%20neck%2C%20and%20blared%20his%20profound%20agony%20at%20the%20disclosure%20of%20what%20three%20women%20of%20the%20minority%20Kuki%20community%20have%20had%20to%20suffer%20directly%20to%20loyal%20and%20ever%20ready%20channel%20watchers%20while%20%E2%80%9Chonourable%E2%80%9D%20parliamentarians%20waited%20for%20him%20in%20the%20two%20%E2%80%9Caugust%E2%80%9D%20houses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0They%20forgot%20that%20this%20is%20still%20the%20month%20of