l%20have%20been%20given%20just%20the%20nationalist%20booster%20to%20further%20fast-forward%20their%20undented%20admiration%20for%20our%20global%20prime%20minister.%20Many%20will%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20hangings%20with%20bated%20breath%2C%20already%20proclaiming%20how%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20sorted%20out%20the%20so-called%20problems%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20fell%20stroke%2C%20he%20has%20obviated%20any%20need%20for%20legislators%20to%20exercise%20their%20brains%20or%20their%20lungs%20in%20parliament%2C%20having%20shared%20his%20miracle%20resolution%20with%20those%20who%20send%20them%20to%20parliament%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20has%20a%20complex%20conundrum%20like%20the%20one%20Manipur%20presents%20been%20sorted%20out%20with%20the%20sort%20of%20dispatch%20the%20kingly%20prime%20minister%20has%20displayed%20to%20the%20astonishment%20of%20the%20world%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20the%20European%20parliament%20can%20likewise%20go%20stew%20themselves%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feuropean-parliament-adopts-resolution-manipur-protection-religious-minorities%5C%22%3Etheir%20unwarranted%20concern%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20our%20little%20secrets%20here%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20them%20not%20pretend%20to%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-in-south-asia-vishwaguru-slogans-meet-regional-realities%5C%22%3EVishwaguru%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20vocation%20reserved%20by%20eternity%20exclusively%20for%20Bharat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20exhilarating%20fact%20that%20our%20parliamentarians%20and%20other%20fussy%20busybodies%20of%20the%20democratic%20system%20fail%20to%20absorb%20is%20that%20Indian%20democracy%20is%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20among%20mere%20hoi%20polloi%20watchdogs%2C%20but%20on%20cloud%20nine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20better%20illustration%20of%20that%20than%20the%20circumstance%20that%20while%20our%20global%20prime%20minister%20is%20often%20seen%20making%20us%20proud%20abroad%20among%20other%20prime%20ministers%20and%20presidents%2C%20corporate%20honchos%20and%20generals%2C%20we%20weakly%20let%20him%20down%20by%20carping%20at%20niggling%20irritants%20like%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELarge%20segments%20of%20old-fashioned%20Indians%20still%20will%20not%20realise%20that%20what%20makes%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnation%E2%80%9D%20great%20is%20not%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20economic%20life%20at%20the%20grass%20roots%2C%20its%20social%20enlightenment%2C%20its%20political%20probity%2C%20the%20independence%20of%20its%20media%2C%20the%20grit%20of%20state%20institutions%20to%20be%20above%20fear%20or%20favour%2C%20the%20unfettered%20productions%20of%20its%20creative%20artists%2C%20writers%2C%20the%20originality%20of%20its%20academicians%2C%20the%20stature%20of%20its%20parliament%2C%20but%20the%20image%20of%20its%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20much%20the%20worse%20for%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20if%20such%20values%20ever%20made%20an%20empire%20of%20any%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690158719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23153053%2FUntitled-design-7-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-manipur-narendra-modi-prime-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20one%20fell%20stroke%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20obviated%20any%20need%20for%20legislators%20to%20exercise%20their%20brains%20or%20lungs%20in%20parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni