and%20smeared%20it%20on%20my%20body%20including%20head%20and%20face.%20I%20filed%20the%20FIR%20the%20next%20day%20since%20I%20was%20busy%20with%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahirwar%20told%20local%20media%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com.%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbhopal%2Fmp-dalit-man-says-face-smeared-with-faeces-accused-detained-8855094%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20alleges%20that%20Patel%20abused%20him%20on%20casteist%20lines%2C%20PTI%20reported.%20Patel%20was%20detained%20on%20Saturday%20following%20Ahirwar%E2%80%99s%20complaint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20incident%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20a%20video%20was%20widely%20circulated%20showing%20a%20man%20allegedly%20urinating%20on%20someone%20from%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20community%20in%20the%20same%20state%E2%80%99s%20Sidhi%20district.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20offending%20man%20has%20since%20been%20identified%20as%20Pravesh%20Shukla.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-man-urinate-tribal-youth-viral-video%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20arrested%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%204%20and%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20him%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20similar%20case%20was%20reported%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Prakasam%20district%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20where%20a%20group%20of%20nine%20young%20men%20allegedly%20assaulted%20and%20then%20urinated%20on%20the%20face%20of%20a%20tribal%20man%20following%20a%20disagreement%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fandhra-pradesh-six-including-three-minors-arrested-for-thrashing-and-urinating-on-tribal-youth-in-ongole%2Farticle67098079.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20men%20and%20three%20minors%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20that%20case%20as%20of%20Friday%2C%20July%2020%20and%20local%20police%20invoked%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Atrocities%20Act%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20in%20Chhatarpur%20have%20also%20invoked%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Atrocities%20Act%20against%20Patel.%20The%20Act%20is%20meant%20to%20protect%20members%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(also%20known%20as%20Dalits)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20which%20are%20historically%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20from%20discrimination.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20case%20is%20being%20registered%20against%20Ramkripal%20Patel%20under%20sections%20294%20(punishment%20for%20obscene%20acts%20or%20words%20in%20public)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Schedule%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20sub-divisional%20officer%20of%20police%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Baghel%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaghel%20added%20that%20Ahirwar%20and%20others%20working%20to%20construct%20a%20drain%20in%20Bikaura%20village%20were%20%E2%80%9Cjoking%20with%20Patel%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Churling%20things%20at%20each%20other%20playfully%E2%80%9D%20following%20which%20Patel%20threw%20faeces%20at%20Ahirwar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690115423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F21134948%2Fbihar-police_pti.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fdalit-man-alleges-obc-man-smeared-faeces-on-him%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20victim%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20local%20panchayat%20fined%20him%20Rs%20600%20after%20he%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20it.%20Police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20accused%20under%20the%20IPC%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Atrocities%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fdalit-man-alleges-obc-man-smeared-faeces-on-him%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sixth%20Person%20Arrested%20in%20Manipur%20Video%20Case%20Is%20a%20Juvenile%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20222528%2Fimage-1149.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Manipur%20police%20has%20arrested%20a%20sixth%20person%20in%20the%20case%20where%20three%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20Thoubal%20district%20on%20May%204.%20All%20six%20arrests%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20the%20video%20showing%20two%20of%20the%20women%20being%20led%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20men%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Ewent%20viral%20on%20July%2019%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Feast-and-northeast%2Fpolice-make-sixth-arrest-in-manipur-disrobing-case-1239670.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20sixth%20person%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20crime%20is%20a%20juvenile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20four%20arrests%20were%20all%20made%20on%20July%2020.%20Chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20facing%20intense%20criticism%20for%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20the%20nearly%20three-month-long%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20had%20tweeted%20the%20news%20of%20the%20first%20arrest%2C%20say