20up%20the%20class%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20good%20kitchen.%20We%20just%20had%20a%20small%20wooden%20table.%20Our%20first%20guest%20was%20an%20Australian%20couple.%20I%20was%20so%20nervous%2C%20my%20hands%20were%20shaking%20and%20I%20was%20also%20sweating.%20I%20even%20dropped%20a%20teacup%2C%20but%20they%20encouraged%20me%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashi%20runs%20cooking%20classes%20to%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324596%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashi%20runs%20cooking%20classes%20to%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20next%20class%2C%20there%20were%20French%20tourists.%20They%20did%20not%20know%20English%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20French.%20They%20would%20look%20at%20my%20face%2C%20I%20would%20look%20at%20theirs!%20If%20they%20said%20%3Cem%3E