ashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashi%20has%20trained%20at%20least%201%2C000%20foreigners%20from%20Italy%2C%20Russia%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Poland%2C%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324609%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashi%20has%20trained%20at%20least%201%2C000%20foreigners%20from%20Italy%2C%20Russia%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Poland%2C%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20teaches%20them%20how%20to%20cook%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lentil%20gravy)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealu%20gobi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(potato%20cauliflower%20stir%20fry)%2C%20paneer%20butter%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(gravy%20cooked%20with%20cottage%20cheese)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echapati%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egatte%20ki%20sabji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20curry%20made%20with%20chickpea%20flour%20sausages)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20cooks%20a%20unique%20kind%20of%20garlic%20cheese%20made%20from%20hung%20curd%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20chopped%20garlic%20which%20is%20applied%20over%20hot%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Echapati%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20served%20with%20tomato%20curry.%20%E2%80%9COur%20guests%20love%20it%2C%E2%