0of%20intervention%2C%20our%20major%20role%20is%20complete%20in%20building%20the%20playground%20and%20we%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20this%20handover%20period%20is%20over%20one%20or%20three%20months%2C%20it%20varies%20based%20on%20where%20the%20playground%20is%20located.%20They%20often%20complete%20building%20the%20playground%20in%20six%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20last%20day%2C%20we%20do%20a%20quality%20check%20with%20the%20corporate%20who%E2%80%99s%20funding%20the%20project%20and%20the%20local%20headmaster%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20playground%20we%E2%80%99ve%20constructed%20meets%20all%20the%20basic%20quality%20measures.%20And%20then%20we%20proceed%20towards%20our%20adoption%20plan.%20We%20identify%20one%20community%20champion.%20It%20could%20be%20anyone%20from%20a%20headmaster%20to%20a%20teacher%20or%20an%20alumni%20of%20that%20school%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20building%20that%20playground%20and%20is%20happy%20to%20volunteer%20their%20time.%20We%20maintain%20correspondence%20with%20them.%20After%20one%20month%2C%20we%20contact%20them%20to%20do%20a%20basic%20check%20on%20how%20children%20are%20playing%20in%20these%20playgrounds.%20We%20have%20a%20questionnaire%20that%20they%20answer%20to%20help%20us%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20playground.%20We%20get%20both%20quantitative%20and%20qualitative%20feedback%20and%20whenever%20we%E2%80%99re%20building%20a%20new%20play%20element%2C%20we%20receive%20some%20extra%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201300px)%20100vw%2C%201300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-7-1689861524.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovative%20playgrounds%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t