uses%20which%20cannot%20be%20seen%20with%20the%20naked%20eye%20but%20are%20useful%20for%20crops.%20We%20term%20them%20as%20friends%20of%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESold%20in%20liquid%20as%20well%20as%20powder%20form%2C%20these%20products%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%20250%20and%20Rs%20400.%20The%20products%20have%20certification%20from%20the%20Central%20Insecticide%20Board%2C%20Faridabad.%20Other%20than%20conventional%20farming%2C%20these%20bio-pesticides%20and%20bio-fertilisers%20can%20also%20be%20used%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324007%2Fvadodara-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-vegetables-at-home-terrace-aquaponics-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponics%20and%20aquaponics%20%3C%2Fa%3Etypes%20of%20farming%2C%20says%20Sangita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-3-1689772156.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20Vidarbha%20Biotech%20Ltd%2C%20Sangita%20sells%2016%20kinds%20of%20bio-pesticides%2C%20bio-fungicides%2C%20and%20bio-fertilisers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-3-1689772156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-3-1689772156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-3-1689772156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-3-1689772156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-3-1689772156-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Through%20Vidarbha%20Biotech%20Ltd%2C%20Sangita%20sells%2016%20kinds%20of%20bio-pesticides%2C%20bio-fungicides%2C%20and%20bio-fertilisers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20use%20bio%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agricultural%20entomologist%20lists%20four%20major%20benefits%20of%20using%20bio-pesticides%20and%20bio-fertilisers%20in%20the%20crop%20instead%20of%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKills%20pests%20and%20prevents%20disease%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESangita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20direct%20advantage%20of%20these%20alternatives%20is%20that%20they%20control%20pests%20and%20diseases%2C%20and%20boost%20nutrients%20in%20soil%20by%20killing%20pests%20in%20their%20larvae%20and%20pupa%20stage.%20This%20prevents%20pests%20from%20spreading%20in%20the%20crop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtects%20seed%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CMicroorganisms%20continue%20to%20secrete%20nutrients%20and%20maintain%20moisture%20near%20seeds%20so%20that%20even%20in%20case%20of%20no%20rain%2C%20it%20will%20prevent%20the%20seeds%20from%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoosts%20soil%20fertility%20and%20maintains%20C%2FN%20ratio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThese%20microorganisms%20also%20make%20the%20soil%20fertile%20by%20increasing%20the%20porosity%20of%20the%20soil.%20It%20also%20helps%20maintain%20the%20carbon-to-nitrogen%20(C%2FN)%20ratio%20in%20the%20soil.%20A%20ratio%20of%2018%3A1%20should%20be%20maintained%20for%20a%20good%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-2-1689772494.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sold%20in%20liquid%20as%20well%20a