all%20assembly%20and%20then%20head%20to%20their%20classes.%20%E2%80%9CI%20teach%20them%20everything%20from%20mathematics%20and%20science%20to%20English%20and%20art.%20I%20also%20conduct%20many%20activities%20like%20gardening%2C%20dancing%2C%20etc%20throughout%20the%20week%20to%20keep%20the%20learning%20wholesome%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%E2%80%99s%20age%20group%20is%20between%20three%20and%2010%20years%20old.%20The%20classes%20go%20up%20to%205%20o%E2%80%99clock%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portia's%20classroom%20in%20Komic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324385%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPortia%20left%20her%20journalism%20career%20to%20become%20a%20teacher%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmother%E2%80%9D%20to%20these%20underprivileged%20children.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Portia%20Putatunda%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20girl%2C%20who%20is%20older%20than%20other%20children%2C%20takes%20one%20class%20at%20my%20school.%20She%20used%20to%20be%20very%20shy.%20But%20today%2C%20she