Fem%3E%20found%20that%20over%20three%20lakh%20disposable%20diapers%20are%20either%20burned%20or%20sent%20to%20landfills%20every%20minute.%20This%20practice%20contributes%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%2C%20and%20pollution%20of%20our%20oceans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20report%20stated%20that%20the%20global%20disposable%20nappy%20industry%20extracts%20over%20248%20million%20barrels%20of%20crude%20oil%20annually%2C%20and%20creates%20over%2038%20million%20tons%20of%20solid%20waste%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20about%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20disposable%20diapers%20was%20Sonika%E2%80%99s%20initiation%20into%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20going%20back.%20Today%2C%20the%20sustainability%20enthusiast%20shares%20her%20experiences%20and%20tips%20on%20zero%20waste%20practices%2C%20sustainable%20parenting%2C%20and%20leading%20an%20environmentally%20conscious%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Started%20thinking%20about%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20future%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F51NxQepHaRQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Sonika%20Bhasin%20started%20living%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20Abir%20was%20born%2C%20our%20lifestyle%20was%20pretty%20wasteful.%20We%20realised%20that%20this%20lifestyle%20was%20not%20good%20for%20Abir%E2%80%99s%20future%20and%20decided%20to%20make%20some%20changes.%20I%20first%20started%20by%20cloth%20diapering%20Abir%20till%20he%20was%20potty%20trained.%20Why%20would%20I%20want%20to%20put%20a%20plastic%20diaper%20full%20of%20toxic%20chemicals%20on%20my%20child%3F%20I%20found%20that%20wet%20wipes%20are%20also%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20so%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20use%20them%3B%20same%20with%20cotton%20balls.%20We%20started%20reusing%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20started%20reading%2C%20she%20discovered%20how%20many%20household%20items%20are%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20slowly%20started%20making%20more%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20think%20that%20cleaners%20and%20detergents%2C%20which%20dissolve%20in%20water%2C%20are%20harmless.%20When%20I%20found%20out%20that%20they%20could%20also%20be%20non-biodegradable%2C%20I%20started%20investigating%20further%20and%20switched%20to%20biodegradable%20detergents.%20When%20Abir%20started%20crawling%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20him%20to%20be%20on%20a%20floor%20that%20was%20mopped%20using%20a%20toxic%20floor%20cleaner.%20So%20I%20started%20buying%20bioenzymes%20and%20later%20made%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20sustainability%20enthusiast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESonika%20then%20started%20eliminating%20plastic%20from%20her%20kitchen%20and%20reducing%20waste.%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abir%20with%20his%20bioenzymes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-scaled.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-1536x2048.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323374%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbir%20loves%20making%20bioenzymes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20composting%20at%20home.%20We%20also%20started%20doing%20package-free%20grocery%20shopping.%20We%20simply%20carry%20bags%20from%20home%20and%20go%20to%20shops%20that%20sell%20loose%20grains%2C%20dry%20fruits%2C%20and%20other%20grocery%20items.%20We%20even%20carry%20containers%20to%20buy%20sweets%2C%20pastries%2C%20curd%2C%20paneer%2C%20etc.%20A%20zero%20waste%20store%20opened%20up%20near%20my%20house%20a%20few%20years%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Sonika%20is%20ensuring%20that%20no%20packaging%20enters%20her%20kitchen.%20She%20always%20carries%20a%20water%20bottle%2C%20napkin%2C%20cutlery%20and%20a%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(box)%20when%20she%20goes%20out.%20She%20even%20carries%20this%20during%20her%20travels%20to%20ensure%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323054%2Fbengaluru-architects-build-zero-waste-sustainable-euroschool-near-national-park%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20750px)%20100vw%2C%20750px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen